      "text": "ふふふ……\nえへへ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehehe…\nEhehe~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.8612874296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 5.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "さくら？\nやけに上機嫌だが何かいいことでもあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura?\nYou seem unusually cheerful. Did something good happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 11.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　サニピが出演するお正月のテレビ番組に\n芸人のホットドッグさんも出るって聞いて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! I heard that on the New Year's TV show where\nSunny Peace will appear‚ the comedian Mr.Hot Dog will also be on…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.7463727315,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、そのことか\n企画コーナーでさくらと羽根つき対決するんだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I see. Is that about the planned section\nwhere Sakura will have a Hanetsuki （Japanese badminton） showdown?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 25.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんです！\n大好きな芸人さんなので共演出来るのが嬉しくて！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right!\nI'm so happy to be co-starring with a comedian I love!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 31
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そういえばみんなは一時期\nレッスンの合間にお笑いのDVDをよく観ていたな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh right‚ everyone used to watch\ncomedy DVDs during breaks between lessons.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃんが自然な笑顔になれるように\nいろいろ試してた頃ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That was when we were trying various things to\nhelp Shizuku-chan have a natural smile.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 42.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "あの時観たDVDが面白くって、それ以来ずっと\n私はホットドッグさんを応援してるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ the time we watched those DVDs and found them funny.\nSince then‚ I've been cheering for Mr.Hot Dog.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "だから共演するって知った時は嬉しくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So when I found out we'd be co-starring‚ I was thrilled!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 53.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんには冷めた目で見られちゃいましたけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Though Rei-chan looked at me skeptically…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 58.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "それで、雫ちゃんから言われたんです！\nお笑い業界は爪痕を残してなんぼ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then‚ Shizuku-chan told me this…\n\"In the comedy industry‚ it's all about leaving an impact…\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 66.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "番組を盛り上げられなかったら\n二度と使ってもらえない厳しい世界だって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"If we can't liven up the show‚\nwe won't get invited back; it's a tough world.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 72.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "だから私、今度の羽根つき対決で\n絶対に爪痕を残したいんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ in this Hanetsuki showdown‚\nI absolutely want to leave an impact!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "さくらはお笑い芸人さんじゃないだろ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura‚ you're not a comedian though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 78.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "でもホットドッグさんとの共演で\n何も出来ずに終わりたくありません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I don't want to end up doing nothing\nin the co-starring with Mr.Hot Dog!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 87.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "お願いします！　私が爪痕を残すために\n羽根つきの特訓に付き合って下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please‚ help me with my Hanetsuki training\nso that I can leave an impact!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 93.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "爪痕はともかく意気込みはよく分かった\n俺で良ければさくらの練習に付き合うよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Leaving an impact aside‚ I get your enthusiasm.\nIf it's okay with me‚ I'll accompany you in practice‚ Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！\n実はもう道具も準備してあるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much!\nActually‚ I've already prepared the props.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 105.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "準備って羽子板と羽根を？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You mean the racket and shuttlecock?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 111.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "それに……じゃじゃーん！\n墨もあります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And… Ta-da!\nI even have ink!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……墨はいらないんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Do we really need the ink?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 118.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-skr015.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ～\n私が勝ったら顔にいたずら書きしますからね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe~ If I win‚\nI'll draw something funny on your face~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_03_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "さくら……楽しそうだな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura… You seem to be having fun…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.5333333333,
