      "text": "（という訳で）\n（さくらと羽根つきの練習をしてみた訳だが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（So‚ that's how it went.）\n（I tried practicing Hanetsuki with Sakura…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 135.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
